本插件用于采集电流、电压、电量、温度值，已知Google Nexus4/Nexus5和中兴红牛V5能够准确的输出电流值。使用前先确定采样率，推荐100ms~1000ms，然后勾选被观测项（电流I/电压U/电量Power/温度Temp）,点Start确定后，会在出参界面显示选中的观测项。
这是一个抓包插件，直接点击Start即可抓包，点击Stop后保存已抓包的内容到文件。抓包文件可用PC上的Wireshark软件分析。
这是一个wakelock的控制插件，当点击Full wakelock时，手机不会主动灭屏，并且手动灭屏了也不会进入休眠状态。当点击Partial wakelock时，手机灭屏后也不会休眠。
这是一个内存填充插件，当点击fill时，会为GT进程在Native层分配xxxMB的内存。GT所占用的内存数在PSS数据中可以体现出来。
GPS采集：点击record开始采集，再点击会停止采集。文件存放在gt日志目录下的gps目录里。\r\nGPS回放：选择gps目录里的文件，点击replay开始，再点击停止。回放需要系统设置如下：1、设置里的位置选项，只打开通过GPS定位，其他关闭。2、开发者选项里选择允许模仿位置。
拖动进度条改变GPS回放的进度后，点击保存即可生效。
使用：检测（结果为OK）->选中被调试的进程->启动调试\n设置：检测（结果NOT OK）->点击更改->点击重启\n注意：无需检测时请点击停止调试，调试完毕时请点击恢复并重启系统还原设置

本插件用于将采集的数据上传到web端进行展示。GT的web资源由Bugly平台提供，Bugly平台可以使用QQ帐号快速登录，使用前请确保:
1.手机上安装了手机QQ
2.在bugly.qq.com注册过产品

This plug-in is used to collect current, voltage, power, temperature, Google Nexus4/Nexus5 and ZTE_Red_Bull_V5 can accurately output current value. Before use to determine the sampling rate, recommended 100ms~1000ms, and then check the observed items (current I / voltage U / electricity)

This is a tcpdump plugin. Press "start" directly to capture network packets. The file that records the network data will be saved until the button "stop" clicked. The saved files can be analysed by wireshark.

This is a wakelock control plug-in, click on the Full wakelock, the phone will not take the initiative off the screen and off the screen manually, it will not go to sleep. When you click Partial wakelock, the phone will not sleep after the off-screen.
This plugin can be used for filling memory. GT will allocate xxxxMB memory in native, if the button "fill" clicked. The total memory occupied by GT can be tracked in pss.

GPS Collection: Click "Record" to start. The collection file is saved in /GT/Log/gps directory.\r\nGPS Replay: Choose a GPS Collection file and click "Replay" to start. The system settings should: 1. only enable the GPS function while others remain disabled in the location services; 2. select the "Allow mock locations" in the Developer options.
Drag seekbar to change replay progress, become effective after click save button.
Usage :Check(if OK)->select App->Start\nSetting:Check(if NOT OK)->Modify->Restart\nNotice :if want resume setting, Resume->Restart
